children.text:
1. Select the quote you want to work on.
2. The rating formulas are in the centre of the page. Adjust the values as required.
3. Run Pricing, will rate and save all of the quote data.
4. Report will generate a xlsx file containing all of the data.
Run pricing as many times as you need. Generate reports after each, in order to compare quotes.
